Package: MPAGE
Type: Package
Title: Module-based Pair-wise Analysis of Gene Expression
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Logan Chen [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Logan Chen <yuelong.chen.btr@gmail.com>
Description: A complete workflow for analyzing RNA modification modules 
    and their dynamic changes across samples. Implements module-based 
    pair-wise analysis of gene expression with PPI network construction,
    module identification, and quantification methods. Provides 
    visualization tools including volcano plots, MA plots, and heatmaps
    for publication-quality figures.
